data.description: Come take a tour of this lovely 5-bedroom 4-bathroom, 3 car garage, amazing retreat nestled on .59 treed acres, within the Walden subdivision and District 38 schools, using our 3D virtual tour! Everywhere you look there are mountain birds and other wildlife!  Pride of ownership is reflected inside this home with its total remodel and modern finishes!  Head inside to a main floor that offers a large living room with great natural light, a formal dining room, a beautiful kitchen with a breakfast bar and eating nook, gorgeous stainless-steel appliances, ample cabinetry, attractive wood floors, and back deck access. The family room is wired for surround sound and includes a wood-burning fireplace for those chilly Colorado nights.  Upstairs offers a master bedroom with ensuite, master bathroom with modern tile backsplash and walk in standing shower, two additional full bedrooms with walk-in closets, a full bathroom with bathtub, and a laundry room. The basement is walk-out and includes two full bedrooms, a full bathroom, and an extremely large entertainment room, perfect for gatherings. Backyard has large decks and a 9’ x 13’ spacious custom-built storage shed with roll-up door. Some other added perks include a New 50-gallon hot water heater, a newer radiant heater boiler, a newer roof, and newer windows, stucco, and siding. This home has been beautifully remodeled offering a modern interior, a spacious basement, and a backyard area perfect for entertaining.  Don’t miss your chance to come take a look!
